---
title: Mushroom 'Steak Diane' with Green Bean Amandine and Roasted Potatoes
description: This retro classic – albeit without the cognac – will bring back memories of visiting old-school steakhouses  where this dish was all the rage. Mushrooms add an extra umami kick, while a green bean amandine and roasted potatoes are the perfect sides for this time-honoured dish!
